{"tid":2357020,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印裔「曼聯英雄」被捕","createTime":"2021-01-07T07:08:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T08:24:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"54665f9b68764f61510ce94f22043ff29b317bff","tid":2357020,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T07:08:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210107/XUXC7BQX4NABRDGPPK7BNIDVIU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210107%2FXUXC7BQX4NABRDGPPK7BNIDVIU%2F&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z%2BNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=1f09d212\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210107%2FXUXC7BQX4NABRDGPPK7BNIDVIU%2F&h=83be7160\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210107/XUXC7BQX4NABRDGPPK7BNIDVIU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n印裔「曼聯英雄」被捕<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】昨日被捕的53人中、包括曾參加九龍西初選的印度裔社工安德里（Jeffrey Andrews，圖），當時他打出「少數族裔都是港人」的口號，最終敗選。這位熱血曼聯球迷一直致力協助居港難民，上月更獲曼聯官方選為「七位曼聯英雄」之一，表揚他在港為難民所作的貢獻，當時他受訪提到「今日很艱難，但明日會有好的時光。香港人加油」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：政治素人登廣告拍片 被指策劃者<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/R_BtqeWsWYpr71z-9eqdW7C1Jeg=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6D5JBGZD3ZCCPO4C7THYWOW3IE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FR_BtqeWsWYpr71z-9eqdW7C1Jeg%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6D5JBGZD3ZCCPO4C7THYWOW3IE.jpg&h=1d0e15dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首名南亞社工 協助難民<br />\n<br />\n現年35歲的安德里是第三代印度裔港人，會考得兩分，其後加入黑社會因搶劫被捕，在社工王惠芬及母親支持下改過自新，成為香港第一名南亞裔社工，更在2009年當選香港傑出青年。去年6月底，他舉行記招交代參與初選時自稱屬「溫和民主派」，主張非暴力抗爭，指自己身為社工明白犯法後果，故主張展開對話。當日獲工黨張超雄等撐場。<br />\n<br />\n初選中他僅獲千票，得票為九龍西中最少，去年聖誕前，這位支持曼聯30年的紅魔老球迷，獲曼聯選出為全球七位對所在地區有貢獻的「曼聯英雄」，並由曼聯領隊蘇斯克查透過視像祝福。。。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"0f7be25e99fd981eac0a908550ed3fcb4a77d0ee","tid":2357020,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T07:09:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c475cdb434d3cff389ab874a0c51420170f003a5","tid":2357020,"uid":295650,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T07:11:04.000Z","msg":"大家都睇住佢..."},{"pid":"083fb0dcd1fe3aac3b99193b0daa98e81ae13522","tid":2357020,"uid":92448,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T07:21:16.000Z","msg":"想知印度媒體點睇"},{"pid":"6ad97457ea31f35a35bfff2751e9d6400e0d55c6","tid":2357020,"uid":86395,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T07:27:52.000Z","msg":"唔反獌了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d652004a9af1dde8c6559adbec34a6dea3e4819","tid":2357020,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T07:29:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0211dbf7f34f80d22d40760e9935e2932d8e3007","tid":2357020,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T07:34:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b6fe41d4394a96d3a54e08fdfa95a716973d6c2","tid":2357020,"uid":138964,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T07:38:09.000Z","msg":"respect曼聯球迷<br />\n<br />\n除左波台獌狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"145e83c14c0be59801297c33e1bafb5103dd7663","tid":2357020,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T08:18:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets